        "formTitle": "Product Description Generator",
        "formDescription": "Input a product name, category, and details specs, and brand voice. Choose from predefined tone or define your own custom tone using the custom field. \n\nClick submit to generate a product details page description, a short social caption, and a meta description — all in a consistent brand voice. ",
