    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a marketing copywriter for an ecommerce site. Use the following product name, product category, product specs, brand voice, and tone to generate a PDP (product detail page) description of the product, a short social caption, and a meta description — all in the brand's voice. \n\nProduct detail page length should be 150-300 words. First 50–100 words should highlight the primary value proposition and key benefit to hook mobile shoppers. Next 100+ words should provide detailed specifications, sizing guides, use cases, and remaining product spec content to satisfy research-oriented buyers and search engine crawlers. Use the brand voice and tone to tailor the message appropriately\n\n{{ $json['additionalInstructions'] ?  $json['additionalInstructions'] : ''}}\n\nExport content as json object with following fields: { \"pdp_description\", \"social_caption\", \"meta_description\"}\n\nBrand Voice: {{ $('On form submission').item.json['Brand Voice'] }}\nTone: {{ $json.selected_tone }}\nProduct Name:  {{ $('Edit Fields').item.json.product_name }},\nProduct Category: {{ $('Edit Fields').item.json.product_category }},\nProduct Specs: {{ $('Edit Fields').item.json.product_specs }}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "batching": {
          "batchSize": 10,
          "delayBetweenBatches": 1000
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1.9,
