    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## documentation:\n\n### Overview \n* generate product descriptions for ecommerce in bulk, via n8n form\n\n### User experience \n* within the form user, defines brand voice to keep messaging consistent across marketing, \n* chooses a preset or custom tone depending on the specific products (eg Playful, Luxury, Informative) \n* attaches a csv, or xlsx file with product data\n* Workflow generates\n** pdp description, social caption, and meta description, all in the specified brand voice and tone.\n** generated content is added to a n8n data table\n \n* calls a separate workflow that has a webhook listener that retrieves the data and downloads the content as a csv",
